items.headline: Welcome to the Homeland Wiki
items.desc: Homeland is a psychological thriller television series which stars Damian Lewis as Gunnery Sergeant Nicholas Brody and Claire Danes as Carrie Mathison, a CIA operations officer who has come to believe that an American Marine, who was held captive by Al-Qaeda as a prisoner of war, was turned by the enemy and now poses a significant risk to national security.  Homeland Wiki is a collaborative encyclopedia for all aspects of this tv show which currently airs on the Showtime channel in the United States.
